        {
            "title": "大埔天賦海灣溋玥3房1,222萬沽 原業主本為單位租客 持貨4個月速賺222萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DrQxitxQpdr_prmKOh8QGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/7e2778ff096322eb747f2b88f049cf91\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%A4%A9%E8%B3%A6%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3%E6%BA%8B%E7%8E%A53%E6%88%BF1-222%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD-%E5%8E%9F%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%AC%E7%82%BA%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2-%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%A84%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%80%9F%E8%B3%BA222%E8%90%AC-082613842.html",
