            "title": "財經｜雷軍：小米(01810)正式啟動AI人才招聘專項",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜雷軍：小米(01810)正式啟動AI人才招聘專項\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜雷軍：小米(01810)正式啟動AI人才招聘專項</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小米(01810)創辦人、董事長兼CEO雷軍發文表示，目前正式啟動AI人才招聘專項。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雷軍表示，小米今年在AI領域研發及資本開支高達160億元人民幣，已在基座大模型、具身智能機械人及手機龍蝦等項目上取得非常大進展。</p></div>",
